MF5AUD.original: ~z~Yes, well, I will not let these men treat you like that again. I'm sorry for letting you down, Roman.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~确实，我不会再让那些人这么对你了。很抱歉之前让你失望了，Roman。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Perhaps. That man who I worked for, Ray Boccino. I was asked to kill him and I did.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~也许吧。那个跟我一起做过事的人，Ray Boccino。我被下令去杀了他，而我也确实杀了他。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~I'm getting married to the beautiful Mallorie. How is the best man?
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~我要娶美丽的Mallorie了。伴郎先生怎么样啊？

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Niko, there you are. Tell me what's happening in the exciting world of the gun for a hire?
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，是你啊。雇佣杀手的刺激世界又发生了什么啊？

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Fantastic cousin. Mallorie is going to make me the happiest groom on earth. How are you?
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~超级棒，堂弟。Mallorie会让我成为世界上最幸福的新郎。你怎么样？

MF5AUD.original: ~z~That's a low blow, NB. Seriously, what're you up to at the moment?
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~正中要害啊，NB。认真点，现在你又在干啥呢？

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Shit NB, I was joking. Who was it this time?
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~我靠，NB，我就开个玩笑。这次是谁？

MF5AUD.original: ~z~That wasn't what I wanted to ask you, I wanted to know what it was like to be kidnapped.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~我不是要问你这个，我要问的是被绑架是怎么样的？

MF5AUD.original: ~z~I don't know, I just met someone in the street. It was weird.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~不知道，我只是在路上碰到了一个人。很奇怪。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~This guy called Ray Boccino has had me working with this guy from the Lost biker gang called Johnny,
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~这个叫Ray Boccino的人让我和失落摩托帮的Johnny合作，

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Thanks, for putting things in perspective, Roman. Later on.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~感谢你能提供不同的观点，Roman。回见。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Maybe, if you give me tales of a womanizing, gambling addict.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~可以考虑，只要你给我讲一个沉溺女色和赌博的故事。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Niko, shit, I hope this guy is paying you good for saving his ass.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，我靠，希望被你救了的这人能多给你点感谢金。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~You are a Bellic, remember, and you can't help playing the field. You don't want her getting jealous.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~你可是Bellic家的，记住，你就是爱脚踏几条船。你也不想她吃醋吧。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Not quite. I'm working for a family out of Alderney called the Pegorinos.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~不是，我在替来自Alderney的Pegorino家族做事。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~I hope you took her back to the apartment and had your way with her, Niko. Did she have nice titties?
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~希望你已经把她带回公寓享用过了，Niko。她奶子大吗？

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Jon Gravelli? The head of the Gambetti crime family. Shit, Niko. This man is very dangerous.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~Jon Gravelli？Gambetti犯罪家族的老大。我靠，Niko，这个人很危险的。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Hello, Niko. How's it going, killed anyone recently?
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~你好，Niko。近况如何啊，有没有又杀了谁？

MF5AUD.original: ~z~This man is nearly dead, cousin. He knows the government agent that Michelle forced me to work for.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~这人就快死了，堂兄。他认识Michelle逼我替他干活的那个政府人物。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~I thought this time would come, Niko, but, to be honest,
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~我就知道会有这一刻，Niko，不过说实话，

MF5AUD.original: ~z~It wasn't like that. You don't get it.
~z~Niko, my cousin. Give me some tales of the Liberty City underworld. I'm curious.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，堂弟啊。给我讲点自由城地下世界的故事吧。我很好奇。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Will you drive me back to the office, cousin? Argh.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~你能送我回车行吗，堂弟？呃啊。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Shit, Niko, you're involved with one of the five families?
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~我靠，Niko，你跟五大家族之一扯上关系了？

MF5AUD.original: ~z~There is no cut of the diamonds, the ice got jacked when we tried to sell them.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~没有钻石的分成了，我们卖钻石的时候钻石被人抢了。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~They say they will give me Darko. You don't know how long I have waited for this, Roman. It is nearly over.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~他们说他们会给我Darko。你不知道我为了这一刻已经等了多久，Roman。就快结束了。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Come on, NB. I do get it. Liberty is a crazy place.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~得了吧，NB。我都懂的。自由城是个疯狂的地方。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Always, Roman. As much as I can at least when I'm doing the bidding of these Alderney gangsters.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~一直这样，Roman。尽力而为嘛，至少在替这些Alderney黑道做事的时候是这样。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Roman, good to speak to you. I needed to talk to a friend
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~Roman，很高兴能和你说话。我需要跟一个朋友聊聊。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~I don't know how I'm so successful with the ladies. They just love me.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~我真的不知道为什么我这么受女性欢迎。她们就是喜欢我。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~I just hope he's got enough power to be able to find Darko Brevic for me.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~我只希望他的力量足够帮我找到Darko Brevic。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Don't get ahead of yourself, Niko. Be careful around these men. Talk to you soon.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~别做力不能及的事情，Niko。和这些人一起的时候当心点。以后再聊。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~There are all types of people here. Most of them ignore you, some of them want to employ you, some of them want to kill you,
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~这里有形形色色的人。大多数会忽略你，部分人想雇佣你，有的人想杀了你，

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Roman, I apologize again for not being there for you. You have done a lot for me since I got here.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~Roman，我再次为没来找你道歉。到美国后你已经帮了我很多了。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Niko, where are you? I'm at the church now! I'm getting married.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，你在哪儿？我现在在教堂了！我要结婚了。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Hello there. Behaving yourself are you, NB?
~z~Roman, you'd never believe it but I met this girl on Craplist.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~Roman，你肯定不敢相信，但我在Craplist约到妹子了。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Wants to be. Keeps talking about being powerful, about getting on the Commission with the five big families.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~他也想啊。一直在说要做大做强，说要加入五大家族所在的委员会。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~He just got out of prison and he hasn't got much but... I made the right decision.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~他才刚出狱，身上也没几个子，不过...我做了正确的选择。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Good, I feel like I am getting close. I have been working for Jon Gravelli.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~挺好的，感觉我已经很接近了。我最近在替Jon Gravelli干活。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~I'm working for this guy, Phil Bell, at the moment. He's better than Ray Boccino.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~我现在在和这个人做事，Phil Bell。他这人比Ray Boccino要好。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~The choice between some titties and your safety would have been difficult for me as well.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~在你和奶子之间选一个的话对我也是个难题。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Roman, can I ask you a question?
~z~This cannot happen without my best man.
~z~The Lost? Those guys are meant to be really dangerous, cousin.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~失落帮？那些人都很危险的，堂弟。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Not when it means me getting beat up and sent to hospital. Come and pick me up, cousin.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~那会儿我也没被人暴揍一顿送进医院啊。过来接我，堂弟。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~It's all sport, NB. Have some fun with her. Later on, cousin. I'm proud of you.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~就当是玩玩吧，NB。祝你玩得愉快。回见，堂弟。我为你骄傲。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~I've got to go, Roman. I'll talk to you soon.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~我得挂了，Roman。我会尽快打给你的。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~A less violent one. I'll speak to you soon, okay?
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~一条没那么暴力的路。我会再和你联系的，好吧？

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Maybe you should come to the cab office and help me out?
~z~You better be better than fine, cousin. Get to the church for 10am and remember to wear some nice clothes.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~你最好比很好还要好，堂弟。早上十点到教堂来，衣服记得穿好点。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~You don't want to get caught up in that shit. Take your cut of the diamonds and get out of there.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~你不会想招上这种事的。拿到你那份钻石的分成就脱身吧。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, the head of the family. Is he a big time gangster like in the movies then?
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~嗯，家族老大。那他是不是像电影里演的那种黑帮大佬一样？

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Don't worry, Roman. I'm on my way.
~z~And at least tell me that you got her titties out? Maybe then your betrayal would be worthwhile.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~有没有摸到她的奶子？摸到的话你的背叛倒还算值得。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Shame on you, Niko Bellic. You should know better than this. Who is she? Who'd you take her for?
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~真是可耻，Niko Bellic。你自己也知道的。她是谁？谁让你绑架她的？

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Some trust-funder called Alex. I don't really like her but it's something to do, isn't it?
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~一个叫Alex的啃老族。我不太喜欢她，不过也是一种消遣，对吧？

MF5AUD.original: ~z~I want you looking good for the wedding.
~z~Great, Niko. I've got my hands full at the moment with these charming money lenders I know.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~真好，Niko。现在我正忙着对付那些友善的债主呢。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~I've been working for Jimmy Pegorino, the head of that Alderney guido family.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~我最近在替Jimmy Pegorino做事，他是Alderney的那个意大利家族的老大。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Roman, you are right about Liberty City. It is a crazy place.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~Roman，关于自由城你说的没错。这是个疯狂的地方。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~running around after these diamonds he stole.
~z~It must be difficult, Niko. Maybe there is another path to take.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~一定很艰难吧，Niko。可能还有其它路可走。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~I can't think who else would. Speak to you soon, cousin.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~我也想不到还有谁能找到了。以后再聊，堂兄。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Thank you, cousin. Remember to wear some nice clothes.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~谢谢你，堂弟。衣服记得穿好点。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~You mean like when you sleep with two girls on one night and they turn out to be mother and daughter?
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~你是说一晚上睡了两个女人，结果她们是母女的那种吗？

MF5AUD.original: ~z~I want you looking good for the happiest day of my life.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~我希望你在我的大喜之日能好看点。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~He was a cockroach - a pest. But I don't know how long I can keep on dealing in death.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~他是个蟑螂，是害虫。但我不知道这种杀人买卖我还能做多久。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~I did everything they said except for give you up, cousin. I was scared shitless.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~他们说的我都照做，除了出卖你，堂弟。我都快吓死了。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Anyway, I was seeing Michelle. I thought you wanted me to date her?
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~再说了，刚才我去找Michelle了。之前不是你想让我去约她吗？

MF5AUD.original: ~z~I'm working with that Irish family. She's some mobster's daughter - Gracie Ancelotti.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~我在给那个爱尔兰家族做事。她是黑帮老大的女儿，Gracie Ancelotti。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~This fucked up Irish family, well some of them.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~这个乱糟糟的爱尔兰家族的几个成员。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~No connections to your friends no chance of your girlfriend finding out.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~不会被朋友看见，不可能被女友发现。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~He should be paranoid. The Feds are after organized crime in a big way.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~他是该多疑点。FIB打击组织犯罪的力度可不小。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Secondly, I don't think that your loan shark friends could hospitalize me. I can look after myself.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~其次，我不觉得你那些高利贷朋友能把我送进医院。我能保护好自己。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Niko, shit. You're fucking with the mob. The Ancelottis are one of the five old families.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，我靠。你丫惹上大家伙了。Ancelotti家族是五大家族之一。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Thank you for taking the time out of your busy schedule to protect me from those crazy loan sharks you attacked, Niko.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~感谢你这个大忙人能抽出时间，从那些你招惹的高利贷疯子手里保护我，Niko。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Your conscience? Have you killed too many people, Niko?
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~你的良知？你是杀了太多人了吗，Niko？

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Paranoid about wire taps and helicopters but he seems legitimate.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~虽然整天担心窃听和直升机监视，但他正经多了。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~That's what I thought. I've had to kidnap this girl and she's a fucking nightmare.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~和我想的一样。我被迫绑架这个女孩，而她他妈是个噩梦。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~I heard there was a war or something on between the Lost and the Angels of Death.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~我听说失落帮好像跟死亡天使开战了。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Look you'll have to have some fun with the nurses because I can't pick you up. See you soon.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~我没法来接你，看来你得和护士们找会儿乐子了。回头见。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~You're shitting me, NB. No fucking way! Who'd you do it with?
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~你不要骗我，NB。这他妈不可能！你跟谁一起干的？

MF5AUD.original: ~z~I hear you were seen out on the town with a sexy young girl. Who is she?
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~听说你在城里跟一个年轻辣妹在一起。她是谁？

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Have you seen this bank heist on the news, NB? That's some crazy shit. I bet you wish you'd pulled off a job like that...
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~你看过这个银行劫案的新闻了吗，NB？实在是太疯狂了。我看你肯定也想干这么一票...

MF5AUD.original: ~z~It's been a fucking hassle and all for nothing.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~这回惹了一身麻烦还空手而归。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Make sure you get lots of beauty sleep. You need to be at the church at 10am though.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~晚上务必要睡得好点。明早十点你就要到教堂了。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~You shouldn't have borrowed money from them in the first place, Roman.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~一开始你就不该问他们借钱的，Roman。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~I don't know nothing about this. Give her back as soon as you can. I've got to go, Niko.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~具体我也不太清楚。尽快把她放了吧。先挂了，Niko。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~I think it's my conscience. I don't know.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~可能是我的良知吧。我不清楚。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Sure Roman, I'll see you at the church. I'm looking forward to it.
~z~I mean like this Dominican looking guy shot up a deal I was trying to make.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~我是说这个多米尼加人先开枪搅乱了我的钻石交易。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Remember to make it clear that you are a red blooded animal though and you won't be tied down
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~不过记得先跟她说好，你是一个血气方刚的猛兽，这样就不会被

MF5AUD.original: ~z~I need to work with these guys. Hopefully they'll be able to find Darko Brevic for me.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~我需要帮他们做事。他们有希望帮我找到Darko Brevic。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~and the other is a heroin addict ex-freedom fighter. Then there's a sister...
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~还有一个是海洛因成瘾的前自由斗士。然后就是妹妹...

MF5AUD.original: ~z~You're an animal, Roman. Nothing can stop you being horny.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~你这个禽兽，Roman。什么时候都能发情。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Her name is Carmen. I met her on Lovemeet.
~z~If she was not a friend of Mallorie's it would be me with the smell of tittie on my breath and you who ended up in hospital.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~要不是因为她是Mallorie的朋友，呼吸里透着她的奶子味的人就会是我，该进医院的就是你了。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~There is the man who chose cooch before his cousin. I hope she was worth it.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~有个人在他堂兄前选了马子，希望那女人是值得的。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Were you an asshole to the people who took you or did you behave yourself?
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~你是在绑匪面前做个混蛋还是乖乖听他的？

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Stay disorganized would be my advice, Niko. Don't let them get you for racketeering.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~建议你保持无组织，Niko。别让他们以涉黑罪逮捕你。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~You're an animal, Roman. Nothing can stop you being horny. I'll see you soon.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~你这个禽兽，Roman，什么时候都能发情。我马上来接你。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~There are four brothers: two are gangsters, one's a cop
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~他们有四兄弟：两个黑道，一个条子，

MF5AUD.original: ~z~He tried to get me to get rid of a friend of his for him but, uh, I liked the friend better.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~他让我帮忙除掉他的一个朋友，不过...我更喜欢他的朋友。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~That is a useful profession considering your job, NB. Good work.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~=对你这个杀手来说还挺有用的嘛，NB。干得好。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Go home and get some sleep then meet me at the church for 10am.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~回家睡个好觉，明早十点来教堂找我。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Sure Roman, I'll see you at the church. I'm looking forward to it.
~z~Firstly Roman, my breath does not smell of titty.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~首先，Roman，我的呼吸里没有奶子味。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~So, he steals the diamonds at the deal and then has to give them back for the girl. What's the big deal?
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~所以就是，他在交易的时候偷走了钻石，然后又为了这女孩把钻石交了回来。那有什么？

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Niko, I'm getting married tomorrow. Can you believe it?
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，明天我就要结婚了。你敢信吗？

MF5AUD.original: ~z~That won't be a problem, Roman. We're not serious. I'll talk to you soon.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~不会有问题的，Roman。我们也就玩玩。我会再跟你聊的。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~some of them want to fuck you. It's mad cousin. Enjoy the ride.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~甚至有人想上你。是很疯狂，堂弟。享受生活吧。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Not much, cousin. I've gone on a date with this girl I met on Lovemeet.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~没什么，堂兄。我跟一个在觅爱网找到的女孩约会了。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Hey Roman. You ever wonder if things are just coincidence or if everything is all planned?
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~喂，Roman。你有没有想过有些事是巧合，还是说都是被计划好的？

MF5AUD.original: ~z~This Dominican looking guy shot the place up.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~被一个多米尼加人开枪搅和了。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~I can tell from your voice that you like her, Cousin. Are you two doing it?
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~听你的声音我就知道你喜欢她，堂弟。你俩好上了吗？

MF5AUD.original: ~z~I hope you will be able to relax when you do finally find him, Niko. Speak soon.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~希望你在找到他之后能够放松下来，Niko。以后聊。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~How was she cousin? Tell me how she was. I wondered about Michelle when I first met her.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~她怎么样，堂弟？告诉我她怎么样。我第一次见到Michelle就对她好奇了。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Then, I've kidnapped this girl and we're handing her over for these same diamonds
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~然后我绑架了这个女孩，用她换回了同一袋钻石作为赎金，

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Niko, I'm getting married tomorrow. Can you believe it?
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，明天我就要结婚了。你敢信吗？

MF5AUD.original: ~z~My heart goes out to you, cousin. I'll talk to you soon.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~我很同情你，堂弟。我会再联系你的。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~A sister? That sounds more my speed than these crazy brothers.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~妹妹？这可比那些疯狂的兄弟要合我胃口多了。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~All the more reason why I should have hooked up with Michelle. Everyone would be a winner.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~那我就更有理由和Michelle在一起了，大家双赢。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~It's not as much of a coincidence as the mother and daughter.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~还没有我说的那对母女来的巧合。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Niko, today is going to be the happiest day of my life.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，今天是我一生中最幸福的日子。

MF5AUD.original: ~z~Who's paying the bills at the moment?
~z~Good, NB. I'll talk to you later on.
~z~The best place to find a woman, NB.
~z~and this Dominican looking guy is there again.
MF5AUD.translated: ~z~结果这个多米尼加人又出现了。
